**Existing Request/Response Structs (Copy for reference):**

| Line | Struct | Purpose |
|------|--------|---------|
| 718 | `DeleteRequest` | Model deletion request |
| 726 | `ShowRequest` | Model info retrieval |
| 762 | `CopyRequest` | Model copying (source → destination) |
| 768 | `PullRequest` | Model download request |
| 789 | `PushRequest` | Model upload request |

**DeleteRequest Structure (lines 718-723):**
